'''杰里·布罗顿'''（{{lang-en|Jerry Brotton}}）是一位英国历史学家，主要研究[[文艺复兴|文艺复兴]]时期。

==生平==
出生于[[英国|英国]]，担任[[伦敦大学玛丽王后学院|伦敦大学玛丽王后学院]]文艺复兴研究中心教授。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00s5m7w|title=Maps: Power, Plunder and Possession|website=[[BBC_Four|BBC Four]]|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123164100/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00s5m7w|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://historicalwriters.org/hwa-crowns-2017/|title=Winners of the HWA Crowns 2017|website=Historical Writers Association|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129221105/https://historicalwriters.org/hwa-crowns-2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年曾作为策展人参加[[威尼斯双年展|威尼斯双年展]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/14/arts/14iht-rartconway14.html|title=Show Highlights the Return of the Loom|website=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|date=2011-06-13|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2019-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720092406/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/14/arts/14iht-rartconway14.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年在[[牛津大学|牛津大学]][[博德利图书馆|博德利图书馆]]作为联合策展人参展。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.finebooksmagazine.com/blog/rare-maps-imaginary-maps-talking-maps-exhibit|title=Rare Maps & Imaginary Maps: "Talking Maps" on Exhibit|website=Fine Books magazine|date=2019-06-26|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201210522/https://www.finebooksmagazine.com/blog/rare-maps-imaginary-maps-talking-maps-exhibit|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.oxfordtimes.co.uk/news/17741479.cutteslowe-walls-history-revealed-in-maps-exhibition/|title=Cutteslowe Walls' history revealed in maps exhibition|website=[[Oxford_Times|Oxford Times]]|date=2019-07-01|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2019-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720200106/https://www.oxfordtimes.co.uk/news/17741479.cutteslowe-walls-history-revealed-in-maps-exhibition/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

曾经为[[BBC广播三台|BBC广播三台]]、[[BBC广播四台|BBC广播四台]]和[[英国广播公司国际频道|英国广播公司国际频道]]制作和录制节目，包括[[莎士比亚|莎士比亚]]、[[聚集区|聚集区]]和[[黄金国|黄金国]]等题材。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/blog/2013/10/why-are-maps-still-so-powerful-bbc-radio-3-free-thinking-festival/|title=Why are maps still so powerful? BBC Radio 3 Free Thinking Festival|website=[[Ordnance_Survey|Ordnance Survey]]|date=2013-10-29|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116010845/http://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/blog/2013/10/why-are-maps-still-so-powerful-bbc-radio-3-free-thinking-festival/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

